Rating: 4
I really enjoyed the dressing with the fish (I used sole) and the red cabbage. I added plenty of cilantro and some chopped red onion to the slaw. Used sunflower seeds since I didn't have pumpkin. I can't wait to use this dressing with fish tacos!! It's a winner.

Rating: 3
Even though I didn't follow this recipe perfectly (due to my own oversights), it was still wonderful. I forgot to garnish with the seeds, so I tried them on the extra slaw. The seeds really add to it! I was a little nervous about the fish, because I have absolutely no experience with fish. I used tilapia, and it was mild and delicious. Great healthy dish.

